</style><h3 id="outline__2" class="wp-block-heading">浩乐生活城24</h3><p>该活动将于hololive SUPER EXPO 2024闭幕式期间公布。在公告PV中，在第一个场地东京巨蛋城之后展示了日本列岛，有六个光柱矗立。</p><p>今后，《Hololive City 24》预计将在关东（东京+？）、东北（仙台？）、东海（名古屋？）、关西（大阪？）、九州（福冈？）共计6个城市举办。 ).马苏。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AP1GczOAeXFJl241XtzIVxrCD6_d8dWfP12wOy0Rlb4XJT5bWyvgbX1pCJ7dwpJG9m6AG0Q3H9lxBjVl5aocxdmd-adOGV04BHXYsqyaAcMImtUiseKdozISwzY53Zy1W1XygUhwfomYZD-o-Y_WSzcjMt71=w1097-h617-s-no-gm" alt=""/></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AP1GczMMt8daHwSvmSw5klgVTETWY4oFQXj7HejLkukbOjlRlVBWg6rLtFr1pEkGf0IhEhZ74JlopChzB0sdY0G1KVtaCq-_Z6kyKtemmQyCj5Z2NmhwitfjXCFp93P2fsaEj1ZYpZ0T2JPLKvrwcdj8USiC=w1097-h617-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：YouTube<br> © 2016 COVER 公司</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>此外，闭幕式上还宣布hololive SUPER EXPO 2024快闪店将在全国6个城市（东京、宫城、大阪、埼玉、爱知、福冈）举办。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="【#hololivefesEXPO24_DAY2】hololive SUPER EXPO 2024 博览会舞台" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/8QoPUb7BA0Y?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="nzIdZb8fYR"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-super-expo-2024-pop-up-store-to-be-held-in-6-cities-in-japan/">Hololive SUPER EXPO 2024快闪店将在全国6个城市举办</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“hololive SUPER EXPO 2024快闪店将在全国6个城市举办” — P2y